Main cyrillic facets realisations

codecvt - folder with codecvt facets
  codecvt_cp1251.hpp - UNICODE<->CP1251 codecvt
  codecvt_cp866.hpp  - UNICODE<->Cp866 codecvt
  mbwcvt.hpp         - UNICODE<->UTF8 C++-style conversion functions

test.cpp - test suite for codecvt (need BOOST_TEST_FRAMEWORK), use
Makefile.mingw (for Windows MinGW) and Makefile for building.

